<section class="glass-card reveal-on-scroll" aria-labelledby="guidelines-title">
  <h2 id="guidelines-title">Swap Guidelines</h2>
  <div class="guidelines-grid">
    <article>
      <h3>Share New Puzzles</h3>
      <p>Add a simple log sheet in the box if you can. A printable log is available <a href="/files/PuzzleExchangeLog.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">here</a>.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h3>Borrow Responsibly</h3>
      <p>Take what you can complete and return so others can rotate through the collection.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h3>Keep Puzzles Complete</h3>
      <p>If pieces are missing, note it clearly so hosts can remove or relabel the box as needed.</p>
    </article>
    <article>
      <h3>Seal Before Returning</h3>
      <p>Use zip bags or secure lids to prevent pieces from being lost during storage and sharing.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
